EN: We plan to invite friends for a picnic during midsummer.

ZH: 仲夏时分，人们会举行篝火晚会。
EN: Bonfire parties are organized during midsummer.

ZH: 在仲夏，人们会燃放烟花庆祝。
EN: Fireworks are set off to celebrate midsummer.

ZH: 仲夏是欣赏烟花绽放的绝佳时机。
EN: Midsummer is the perfect time to enjoy the blooming fireworks.

ZH: 许多人在仲夏期间喜欢在户外露营。
EN: Many people enjoy camping outdoors during midsummer.

ZH: 去海边度假是仲夏的理想选择。
EN: Going on a seaside vacation is an ideal choice for midsummer.

ZH: 仲夏是观赏日出和日落的好时机。
EN: Midsummer is a good time to admire both sunrise and sunset.

ZH: 在仲夏期间，人们会穿上轻薄的衣服。
EN: People wear light and thin clothes during midsummer.

ZH: 仲夏时节，可以品尝到各式各样的水果。
EN: Various types of fruits can be tasted during midsummer.

ZH: 仲夏是沐浴阳光和海风的季节。
EN: Midsummer is the season to bask in the sunlight and sea breeze.

ZH: 在仲夏望月，人们赏心悦目。
EN: People enjoy the beauty of the moon during midsummer.

ZH: 在仲夏，天空晴朗，很适合观星。
EN: The sky is clear during midsummer, making it perfect for star-gazing.

ZH: 在仲夏，郊外的草地上开满了野花。
EN: Wildflowers bloom across the meadows in the midsummer.

ZH: 仲夏是户外活动最为活跃的季节。
EN: Midsummer is the most active season for outdoor activities.
